description: Great tasting and healthy Açaí Bowls, Smoothies and Fresh Juices! The Açaí Berry is a Brazilian seed fruit known for being rich in antioxidants and Omega 3s. This delicious Superfruit is the base for all of our fresh and natural bowls and smoothies. The Açaí Bowl can be enjoyed as a treat or with a protein add on can become a meal. Originally a favorite in Hawaii, we are proud to be one of the first serving them here in Las Vegas.We are a Mobile Food Truck, fully self contained and equipped to cater birthday parties, weddings, corporate events and more
name: Bowlology
